rows.label: qst201413_msg0001
rows.name: Are you two still up?

rows.label: qst201413_msg0002
rows.name:
We're trying to decide who has more
Girl Power through girl talk.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0003
rows.name: Since you're here, Mei, be our judge.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0004
rows.name: Fine. I'll be the one to judge you.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0005
rows.name:
You're full of energy for
this late at night, Mei.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0006
rows.name:
Hmph... I am one who
lives in the darkness...

rows.label: qst201413_msg0007
rows.name: A child of the night, the Nacht Klan!

rows.label: qst201413_msg0008
rows.name: Naht... Sorry, what did you say?

rows.label: qst201413_msg0009
rows.name: The Nacht Klan.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0010
rows.name:
The power of darkness is the
mark of the Nacht Klan,
usable only by the chosen.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0011
rows.name:
Only the Licht Klan, the children
of light, can oppose us.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0012
rows.name:
Until the day of the Heiliger
Krieg, the holy war where
darkness and light clash...

rows.label: qst201413_msg0013
rows.name:
We build our power, watch
each other's movements, and
keep each other in check.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0014
rows.name: And when we are victorious...

rows.label: qst201413_msg0015
rows.name:
A new world ruled by the Nachtgott,
the god of night, will be born!

rows.label: qst201413_msg0016
rows.name:
Ah, I can't wait for
that day to come...

rows.label: qst201413_msg0017
rows.name: Hikari, do you understand any of this?

rows.label: qst201413_msg0018
rows.name: Not a single word.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0019
rows.name:
I've never met anyone like
her, even 500 years ago...

rows.label: qst201413_msg0020
rows.name:
It's like... she's living
in a different world.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0021
rows.name: Yeah...
